text: Lachlan (or Lauchlan) Mackinnon (or MacKinnon or McKinnon) may refer to: * Sir Lachlan Mackinnon (clan chief) (died c.1634), chief of the Scottish Highland clan Mackinnon * Lauchlan Bellingham Mackinnon (1814–1877), Member of Parliament for Rye, Sussex, England * Lauchlan Mackinnon (1817–1888), an Australian pastoralist, politician and newspaper proprietor * Lachlan Donald Ian Mackinnon (1882–1948), a Royal Navy officer * Lachlan Mackinnon (born 1956), a Scottish poet, critic and literary journalist
title: Lachlan Mackinnon (disambiguation)
